title: Real Humans S1 Ep6
description:
Real Humans S1 Ep6

Sly Leo - In a parallel present day, robots have become so human it is barely possible to distinguish them from real people. In this episode, Leo is weak, but does everything he can to get to Mimi's house, where Matilda is beginning to uncover the truth about Anita. When Bea arrives at Roger's job with a black eye, she cajoles him into taking her in. Lennart is offered the chance to make a hubot copy of himself. But does he want to? Stars Andreas Wilson, Lisette Pagler and Pia Halvorsen. 

From Sweden, in Swedish 

Subtitles by SBS AU TV
